rdpc v3.0 - README [RDP Management Console]


Description :
when number of accesses to RDP gets high, managment gets hard, so in this time you can use this program for managing windows servers. By using this program you can select your server from menu and connect to server without password.


Dependencies:
	0. rdesktop
	1. ping
	2. mkdir
	3. cp
	4. rm
	5. whoami
	6. ping
	7. ssh
	8. cat
	9. nano


Install rdpc v3.0:
	0. chmod +x install.sh
	1. sudo ./install.sh -i


Usage rdpc v3.0:
	0. run program and edit your database
	1. run program and connect to your servers


Uninstall rdpc v3.0:
	0. chmod +x install.sh
	1. sudo ./install -u


Tested rdpc on :
	0. LMDE2 mate desktop - 3.16.0-4-amd64
	1. chromixium 1.5 - 3.13.0-66-generic


Notes:
	0. run this program just using root user or sudo
	1. defaul password is 'rdpc'
	2. run program and edit your database
